{"tid":1841584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"忽發奇想 拉攏心理戰法","createTime":"2020-01-25T10:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T10:59:33.000Z","uid":231766,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e016ae1bc37b6f21826a17933c5e0c1f4239264f","tid":1841584,"uid":231766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:08:57.000Z","msg":"而家我地無論用咩理由去集會/遊行，只要打住抗肺炎，禁止支那狗落去播毒嘅旗號，不論集會式，定前線火魔（例如係高鐵站附近用火魔，再打住封關旗號黎合理化火魔。）其實社會上好多聲音唔少淺黃都會覺得火魔仲係未完全接受到，只係會話理解，咁呢個時候就要靠暗黑兵法拉攏同合理化，因為我地要對准政權先用火魔，類似咁樣。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 絕不支持呢個時勢用武力，會失民意㗎 千奇唔好，好暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d42a8b225b69d8fc336ac498658516babde3270","tid":1841584,"uid":231766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:23:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a982a5b6bcc6eda95d7eadc641bea73f7a5a9799","tid":1841584,"uid":223006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:28:26.000Z","msg":"罷工啦仲出黎"},{"pid":"ba1512322733d55c3d5763e6460c37ee8143aa0f","tid":1841584,"uid":231766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:29:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad12ef732df8b972d9bba9ace11bb94f2115bda","tid":1841584,"uid":231766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a982a5b6bcc6eda95d7eadc641bea73f7a5a9799","tid":1841584,"uid":223006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:28:26.000Z","msg":"罷工啦仲出黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:30:10.000Z","msg":"罷工還罷工，講緊合理化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 絕對支持罷工癱瘓，但未做到嘅時候咪要加速"},{"pid":"e32a59f04f03465a413e04beeea886d82b4f9161","tid":1841584,"uid":209310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:59:33.000Z","